[
  {
    "startTime": 3.0,
    "endTime": 6.1,
    "text": "Och, Fergus, no weapons on the table."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.3,
    "endTime": 10.5,
    "text": "Can I shoot an arrow? Can I? Can I? Can I? Can I? Please, can I?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.7,
    "endTime": 12.2,
    "text": "Not with that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.2,
    "endTime": 16.2,
    "text": "Why not use your very own?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.5,
    "endTime": 18.84,
    "text": "Happy birthday, my wee darling."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.6,
    "endTime": 24.799,
    "text": "Now, there's a good girl."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.879,
    "endTime": 28.719,
    "text": "Draw all the way back now to your cheek. That's right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.92,
    "endTime": 31.32,
    "text": "Keep both eyes open."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.4,
    "endTime": 32.958999999999996,
    "text": "And..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.04,
    "endTime": 34.04,
    "text": "Loose!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.639,
    "endTime": 36.639,
    "text": "I missed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.72,
    "endTime": 38.24,
    "text": "Go and fetch it, then."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.279,
    "endTime": 43.32,
    "text": "A bow, Fergus? She's a lady."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.5,
    "endTime": 84.68,
    "text": "A will-o'-the-wisp."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.0,
    "endTime": 94.0,
    "text": "They are real."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.0,
    "endTime": 103.0,
    "text": "Merida!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.0,
    "endTime": 104.9,
    "text": "Come on, sweetheart."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.0,
    "endTime": 105.8,
    "text": "We're leaving now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.8,
    "endTime": 108.89999999999999,
    "text": "I saw a wisp."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.9,
    "endTime": 110.10000000000001,
    "text": "I saw a wisp."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.3,
    "endTime": 111.2,
    "text": "A wisp?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.4,
    "endTime": 117.0,
    "text": "You know, some say that will-o'-the-wisps lead you to your fate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.0,
    "endTime": 118.519,
    "text": "I think it's done, Daddy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.519,
    "endTime": 119.519,
    "text": "Yeah, are you sure?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.599,
    "endTime": 120.5,
    "text": "Mm-hmm."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.5,
    "endTime": 121.68,
    "text": "Absolutely positive?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.76,
    "endTime": 122.76,
    "text": "Yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.839,
    "endTime": 126.0,
    "text": "Okay, I'm about to put this spoon in my..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.08,
    "endTime": 127.08,
    "text": "Wait!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.36,
    "endTime": 132.36,
    "text": "Done."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.839,
    "endTime": 136.839,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.919,
    "endTime": 142.16000000000003,
    "text": "Well, sweetheart, this is the best gumbo I've ever tasted."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.24,
    "endTime": 143.0,
    "text": "Come here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.1,
    "endTime": 145.6,
    "text": "Eudora, our little girl's got a gift."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.6,
    "endTime": 146.88,
    "text": "Mmm-hmm. I could've told you that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.96,
    "endTime": 150.279,
    "text": "A gift this special just gotta be shared."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 150.36,
    "endTime": 153.03900000000002,
    "text": "Hey, everybody, I made gumbo."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.119,
    "endTime": 154.679,
    "text": "Ooh, that smells good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.759,
    "endTime": 156.88,
    "text": "I got some hush puppies, Tiana. Here I come."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.96,
    "endTime": 162.75900000000001,
    "text": "You know, the thing about good food, it brings folks together from all walks of life."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.839,
    "endTime": 167.32,
    "text": "It warms them right up and it puts little smiles on their faces."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.399,
    "endTime": 169.8,
    "text": "And when I open up my own restaurant,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.88,
    "endTime": 174.839,
    "text": "I tell you, people are gonna line up from miles around just to get a taste of my food."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.96,
    "endTime": 176.6,
    "text": "Our food."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.679,
    "endTime": 178.199,
    "text": "That's right, baby."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.279,
    "endTime": 180.72,
    "text": "Our food."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.759,
    "endTime": 188.279,
    "text": "Daddy, look."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.36,
    "endTime": 189.36,
    "text": "Where are you going?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.44,
    "endTime": 195.919,
    "text": "Charlotte's fairy tale book said, if you make a wish on the evening star, it's sure to come true."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.0,
    "endTime": 198.839,
    "text": "Hmm. Well, you wish on that star, sweetheart."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.919,
    "endTime": 202.60000000000002,
    "text": "Yes, you wish and you dream with all your little heart."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.72,
    "endTime": 208.039,
    "text": "But you remember, Tiana, that old star can only take you part of the way."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.119,
    "endTime": 211.24,
    "text": "You gotta help it along with some hard work of your own."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.32,
    "endTime": 215.19899999999998,
    "text": "And then, yeah, you can do anything you set your mind to."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.679,
    "endTime": 219.479,
    "text": "Just promise your daddy one thing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.559,
    "endTime": 224.35999999999999,
    "text": "That you'll never, ever lose sight of what's really important."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.32,
    "endTime": 226.32,
    "text": "Okay?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.52,
    "endTime": 231.479,
    "text": "See you in the morning, baby cakes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.119,
    "endTime": 234.119,
    "text": "Get some sleep."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.039,
    "endTime": 250.039,
    "text": "Please, please, please."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 406.0,
    "endTime": 409.44,
    "text": "The magic of the golden flower healed the queen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 411.44,
    "endTime": 416.44,
    "text": "A healthy baby girl, a princess was born with beautiful golden hair."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 425.44,
    "endTime": 426.44,
    "text": "I'll give you a hint."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 427.44,
    "endTime": 427.9,
    "text": "That's Rapunzel."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 430.2,
    "endTime": 435.44,
    "text": "To celebrate her birth, the king and queen launched a flying lantern into the sky."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 440.3,
    "endTime": 443.44,
    "text": "And for that one moment, everything was perfect."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 446.44,
    "endTime": 447.44,
    "text": "And then that moment ended."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 449.4,
    "endTime": 453.44,
    "text": "♪Flower, gleam and glow ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 455.44,
    "endTime": 458.44,
    "text": "♪Let your power shine ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 459.44,
    "endTime": 463.0,
    "text": "♪Make the clock ring ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 468.3,
    "endTime": 472.44,
    "text": "Gothel broke into the castle, stole the child, and just like that, gone."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 475.2,
    "endTime": 478.5,
    "text": "The kingdom searched and searched, but they could not find the princess."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 478.7,
    "endTime": 483.59999999999997,
    "text": "For deep within the forest, in a hidden tower, Gothel raised the child as her own."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 483.7,
    "endTime": 486.4,
    "text": "♪Save what has been lost ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 486.7,
    "endTime": 490.0,
    "text": "♪Bring back what once was mine♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 490.44,
    "endTime": 493.5,
    "text": "♪What once was mine♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 493.6,
    "endTime": 499.3,
    "text": "Gothel had found her new magic flower, but this time, she was determined to keep it hidden."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 499.44,
    "endTime": 501.7,
    "text": "Why can't I go outside?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 501.9,
    "endTime": 507.29999999999995,
    "text": "The outside world is a dangerous place, filled with horrible, selfish people."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 507.44,
    "endTime": 510.3,
    "text": "You must stay here, where you're safe."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 510.44,
    "endTime": 511.9,
    "text": "Do you understand, Flower?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 512.2,
    "endTime": 516.7,
    "text": "Yes, Mommy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 516.9,
    "endTime": 524.6,
    "text": "But the walls of that tower could not hide everything."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 524.8,
    "endTime": 535.0,
    "text": "Each year on her birthday, the king and queen released thousands of lanterns into the sky, in hope that one day, their lost princess would return."
  }
]